{"tid":116270,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得讀書好大壓力？","createTime":"2017-02-11T09:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T17:33:31.000Z","uid":67209,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29437e16c80548bd266242ddee61f3b7fbdf628f","tid":116270,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"其實都只係岩岩開sem<br />\nD projects 開始一個接一個<br />\n又開始被人free ride<br />\n教左3、4個禮拜書 <br />\nD野又開始跟唔到<br />\nAssignments 又愈來愈多<br />\nD同學又博盡 個個學霸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個莊又愈來愈多野搞<br />\n想今個sem努力d追返gpa 又開始力不從心<br />\n每一日都好忙 但仲要應酬其他野<br />\n屋企人又無啦啦成日嗌交<br />\n朋友又冇時間見 人際關係又開始出現問題<br />\n女又溝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訂立左既目標又開始距離愈來愈遠<br />\n我覺得自己真係一舊垃圾<br />\n生存係世界上侮辱左個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93262eb69e70d3556a639f35762eff51be7dce7","tid":116270,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都只係岩岩開sem<br />\nD projects 開始一個接一個<br />\n又開始被人free ride<br />\n教左3、4個禮拜書 <br />\nD野又開始跟唔到<br />\nAssignments 又愈來愈多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">D同學又博盡 個個學霸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n個莊又愈來愈多野搞<br />\n想今個sem努力d追返gpa 又開始力不從心<br />\n每一日都好忙 但仲要應酬其他野<br />\n屋企人又無啦啦成日嗌交<br />\n朋友又冇時間見 人際關係又開始出現問題<br />\n女又溝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訂立左既目標又開始距離愈來愈遠<br />\n我覺得自己真係一舊垃圾<br />\n生存係世界上侮辱左個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你讀緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ceeae0a9c6c1cf84567d6f0eb6bfeec80408eda","tid":116270,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"諗起條學債已經想跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d986754402367d4360a626eee