ss=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家目標唔同，佢地HEA係正常<br />\n冇咩好覺得頹啵"},{"pid":"094f4864e59f5ffeccff8a5f8548881e8d7135ce","tid":116270,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到有D無讀上去既FD反而活得仲自在<br />\n有時會諗自己究竟追求緊D乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學問<br />\n有認真讀過大學，談吐、見識都高好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其係hku, <del>cu</del><br />\n出黎真係無咁柒</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊垃圾asso 好多中學fd都係讀ive算好似日日都好輕鬆咁真係會諗自己咁辛苦追gpa做乜</blockquote><br />\nAsso=all or nothing</blockquote><br />\n其實求合格嘅話你都可以HEA<br />\nIve應該好難又HEA又GPA高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自問想入u 覺得以前真係哂左太多時間 到認清自己想要d乜個時已經中六 <br />\n見佢地個個都無打算讀上去 得自己好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學吓自己一個啦 仲係細路咩on9"},{"pid":"ca672cf677692f75c875c6244040a0826b3f15e1","tid":116270,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申先asso狗岩岩好grad到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事關我之前係quit hd再報另一個asso<br />\n所以我基本上年紀係大過曬所有人<br />\n<br />\n果陣社會既事佔左我好大部分時間同精神<br />\n影響到我不停諗學生身份其實好困身<br />\n1.已經quit左一次唔可以再quit<br />\n2.讀左咁耐都用左唔少錢<br />\n搞到我完全冇心機讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我之前hd果年浪費左屋企幾皮野已經好內疚所以本身冇問屋企攞要靠自己番pt<br />\n咁我番既係d office呀之類<br />\n我竟然番工係舒服同開心過番學上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直接d講我唔再選擇讀topup出左黎做野<br />\n表現仲幾好間公司名仲呃得下人Tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人能力我唔否認可以係讀書度表現出黎<br />\n但一定唔係全部<br />\n我而加果度有d都係大學生仲要應該係讀書勁果d人黎<br />\n但做野成日都唔撚記得做到好亂做果幾個月都不停問問問<br />\n<br />\n相反讀書廢物既我好早已經pickup曬<br />\nGrad左我都有諗過不如夾硬讀上去<br />\n<br />\n但so far我冇後悔繼續做asso狗而唔係大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我認我人生係好撚-6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42748966c862c03b0cff62cb1f894b6d82291473","tid":116270,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"補充多句<br />\n最緊要係你知自己想點而唔係社會/身邊既人想你點"},{"pid":"182fc7a036e88e295614dbb32e12f7c4c4965520","tid":116270,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到有D無讀上去既FD反而活得仲自在<br />\n有時會諗自己究竟追求緊D乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學問<br />\n有認真讀過大學，談吐、見識都高好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其係hku, <del>cu</del><br />\n出黎真係無咁柒</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊垃圾asso 好多中學fd都係讀ive算好似日日都好輕鬆咁真係會諗自己咁辛苦追gpa做乜</blockquote><br />\nAsso=all or nothing</blockquote><br />\n其實求合格嘅話你都可以HEA<br />\nIve應該好難又HEA又GPA高</blockquote><br />\n早兩年讀ive 自問無咩溫書<br />\n學都少番 成日叫人拍卡<br />\nCgpa 過3.4入番u了 <br />\n<br />\n奉勸認真讀又唔高gpa果d人可以放棄<br />\n就算比你地入得番u都係收硬皮"},{"pid":"8ff5f292121095f53af4bd0f80103234e4fd3ce7","tid":116270,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到有D無讀上去既FD反而活得仲自在<br />\n有時會諗自己究竟追求緊D乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學問<br />\n有認真讀過大學，談吐、見識都高好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其係hku, <del>cu</del><br />\n出黎真係無咁柒</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊垃圾asso 好多中學fd都係讀iv